-------------

Here the main idea is to play with fast rising frequencies (using Saws) and to apply on them a multiplication [0;1] enveloppe and then play those changing frequencies with a (Tri) generator so to get some interesting percussive sounds.
Using a gate to modify the attack of the multiplication envelope creates interesting glitches. 

Enjoy,
